description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare The Aliens Are Coming Edition!

Dave & Tim discuss the outpouring of UFO information or disinformation being shared in mainstream news media this week with a look and listen at the audio from news sources with surprising thoughts on the topic of, ARE WE ALONE? 

Plus Ghosts of Waverly Hills, An Undead Army in Russia, Satanic Panic and more and a BRAND NEW Theater of the Mind from Jason Offutt. 

Come see Dave LIVE this weekend here: https://bit.ly/3eYuOz5
